summary: Healthpeak Properties, Inc. (NYSE: DOC): A Leading Healthcare-Focused REIT SAN FRANCISCO, June 10, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Healthpeak Properties, Inc. (NYSE: DOC) is a fully integrated real estate investment trust (REIT) and S&P 500 company. Healthpeak owns, operates, and develops high-quality real estate focused on healthcare discovery and delivery.
